cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a new building block for deep neural networks specifically for image recognition tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the effectiveness of error back-propagation in learning multiple epitomic layers in a supervised fashion, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a new method for computing responses invariant to small translations, which could fall under the categories of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed method on image classification tasks, which could also fall under the category of cs.CL (Computation and Language).
